headline: Assessing Home Depot (HD) Valuation After Recent Mixed Share Price Performance
summary: Home Depot (HD) shares have moved in mixed fashion recently, with a gain of about 4% over the past month and a 4% decline over the past 3 months, drawing fresh attention to its valuation. See our latest analysis for Home Depot. At a share price of $359.56, Home Depot’s recent 7 day share price return of 4.49% and 30 day share price return of 4.14% contrast with a 1 year total shareholder return decline of 4.82%, hinting that short term momentum is improving while longer term returns remain...
